{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1008,"text":"I am failing as a woman,"},{"time":2832,"text":"I am failing as a feminist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5452,"text":"I have passionate opinions\nabout gender equality,"},{"time":8229,"text":"but I worry that to freely accept\nthe label of \"feminist,\""},{"time":12314,"text":"would not be fair to good feminists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15184,"text":"I'm a feminist, but I'm a rather bad one."},{"time":17581,"text":"Oh, so I call myself a Bad Feminist."},{"time":20469,"text":"Or at least, I wrote an essay,"},{"time":22826,"text":"and then I wrote a book\ncalled \"Bad Feminist,\""},{"time":25025,"text":"and then in interviews, people started\ncalling me The Bad Feminist."},{"time":28485,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29675,"text":"So, what started as a bit\nof an inside joke with myself"},{"time":33736,"text":"and a willful provocation,"},{"time":35441,"text":"has become a thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37996,"text":"Let me take a step back."},{"time":40076,"text":"When I was younger,"},{"time":41336,"text":"mostly in my teens and 20s,"},{"time":43273,"text":"I had strange ideas about feminists"},{"time":45702,"text":"as hairy, angry, man-hating,\nsex-hating women --"},{"time":49502,"text":"as if those are bad things."},{"time":51105,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":54978,"text":"These days, I look at how\nwomen are treated the world over,"},{"time":58440,"text":"and anger, in particular, seems\nlike a perfectly reasonable response."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62750,"text":"But back then,"},{"time":64519,"text":"I worried about the tone people used\n"},{"time":66322,"text":"when suggesting I might be a feminist."},{"time":69322,"text":"The feminist label was an accusation,"},{"time":71904,"text":"it was an \"F\" word, and not a nice one."},{"time":74762,"text":"I was labeled a woman\nwho doesn't play by the rules,"},{"time":77682,"text":"who expects too much,"},{"time":79327,"text":"who thinks far too highly of myself,"},{"time":81344,"text":"by daring to believe I'm equal --\n(Coughs) -- superior to a man."},{"time":86040,"text":"You don't want to be that rebel woman,"},{"time":87909,"text":"until you realize that you\nvery much are that woman,"},{"time":90418,"text":"and cannot imagine being anyone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93344,"text":"As I got older, I began to accept"},{"time":95388,"text":"that I am, indeed, a feminist,\nand a proud one."},{"time":98745,"text":"I hold certain truths to be self-evident:"},{"time":101563,"text":"Women are equal to men."},{"time":104039,"text":"We deserve equal pay for equal work."},{"time":106844,"text":"We have the right to move\nthrough the world as we choose,"},{"time":109852,"text":"free from harassment or violence."},{"time":112233,"text":"We have the right to easy,\naffordable access to birth control,"},{"time":115811,"text":"and reproductive services."},{"time":117732,"text":"We have the right to make choices\nabout our bodies,"},{"time":120327,"text":"free from legislative oversight\nor evangelical doctrine."},{"time":124504,"text":"We have the right to respect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126679,"text":"There's more."},{"time":127909,"text":"When we talk about the needs of women,"},{"time":130148,"text":"we have to consider\nthe other identities we inhabit."},{"time":133577,"text":"We are not just women."},{"time":135518,"text":"We are people with different bodies,"},{"time":137389,"text":"gender expressions, faiths, sexualities,"},{"time":140428,"text":"class backgrounds, abilities,\nand so much more."},{"time":143708,"text":"We need to take into account"},{"time":145129,"text":"these differences and how they affect us,"},{"time":147589,"text":"as much as we account for\nwhat we have in common."},{"time":150680,"text":"Without this kind of inclusion,\nour feminism is nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155220,"text":"I hold these truths to be self-evident,\nbut let me be clear:"},{"time":158895,"text":"I'm a mess."},{"time":160056,"text":"I am full of contradictions."},{"time":162337,"text":"There are many ways in which\nI'm doing feminism wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165876,"text":"I have another confession."},{"time":167416,"text":"When I drive to work, I listen\nto thuggish rap at a very loud volume."},{"time":171776,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":173307,"text":"Even though the lyrics\nare degrading to women --"},{"time":175660,"text":"these lyrics offend me to my core --"},{"time":178479,"text":"the classic Yin Yang Twins\nsong \"Salt Shaker\" --"},{"time":181503,"text":"it is amazing."},{"time":182979,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":185469,"text":"\"Make it work with your wet t-shirt."},{"time":188421,"text":"Bitch, you gotta shake it\n'til your camel starts to hurt!\""},{"time":192205,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":193387,"text":"Think about it."},{"time":194436,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":197348,"text":"Poetry, right?"},{"time":198690,"text":"I am utterly mortified\nby my music choices."},{"time":202374,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204310,"text":"I firmly believe in man work,"},{"time":206618,"text":"which is anything I don't\nwant to do, including --"},{"time":209051,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":210956,"text":"all domestic tasks,"},{"time":213134,"text":"but also: bug killing, trash removal,\nlawn care and vehicle maintenance."},{"time":218014,"text":"I want no part of any of that."},{"time":219905,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":221002,"text":"Pink is my favorite color."},{"time":222923,"text":"I enjoy fashion magazines\nand pretty things."},{"time":225975,"text":"I watch \"The Bachelor\"\nand romantic comedies,"},{"time":228302,"text":"and I have absurd fantasies\nabout fairy tales coming true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232121,"text":"Some of my transgressions\nare more flagrant."},{"time":234914,"text":"If a woman wants to take\nher husband's name,"},{"time":237304,"text":"that is her choice, and it is not\nmy place to judge."},{"time":240622,"text":"If a woman chooses to stay home\nto raise her children,"},{"time":243622,"text":"I embrace that choice, too."},{"time":245737,"text":"The problem is not that she makes herself\neconomically vulnerable in that choice;"},{"time":249832,"text":"the problem is that our society is set up\n"},{"time":252002,"text":"to make women economically vulnerable\nwhen they choose."},{"time":254982,"text":"Let's deal with that."},{"time":257601,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263413,"text":"I reject the mainstream feminism"},{"time":265508,"text":"that has historically ignored\nor deflected the needs"},{"time":268159,"text":"of women of color, working-class women,\nqueer women and transgender women,"},{"time":272571,"text":"in favor of supporting white, middle-\nand upper-class straight women."},{"time":275968,"text":"Listen, if that's good feminism --\nI am a very bad feminist."},{"time":279648,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280762,"text":"There is also this:"},{"time":282238,"text":"As a feminist, I feel a lot of pressure."},{"time":284984,"text":"We have this tendency to put\nvisible feminists on a pedestal."},{"time":288677,"text":"We expect them to pose perfectly."},{"time":291287,"text":"When they disappoint us,"},{"time":292471,"text":"we gleefully knock them\nfrom the very pedestal we put them on."},{"time":295957,"text":"Like I said, I am a mess --"},{"time":298016,"text":"consider me knocked off that pedestal\n"},{"time":299846,"text":"before you ever try to put me up there."},{"time":301867,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":303374,"text":"Too many women,"},{"time":304458,"text":"particularly groundbreaking women\nand industry leaders,"},{"time":307507,"text":"are afraid to be labeled as feminists."},{"time":309869,"text":"They're afraid to stand up and say,\n\"Yes, I am a feminist,\""},{"time":313599,"text":"for fear of what that label means,"},{"time":315868,"text":"for fear of being unable to live up to\nunrealistic expectations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320569,"text":"Take, for example, Beyoncé,\nor as I call her, The Goddess."},{"time":324365,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":326325,"text":"She has emerged, in recent years,\nas a visible feminist."},{"time":329781,"text":"At the 2014 MTV Video Music Awards,"},{"time":332622,"text":"she performed in front of the word\n\"feminist\" 10 feet high."},{"time":336412,"text":"It was a glorious spectacle to see\n"},{"time":338643,"text":"this pop star openly embracing feminism"},{"time":341643,"text":"and letting young women and men know"},{"time":343396,"text":"that being a feminist\nis something to celebrate."},{"time":346985,"text":"As the moment faded, cultural critics\nbegan endlessly debating"},{"time":350668,"text":"whether or not Beyoncé was,\nindeed, a feminist."},{"time":353693,"text":"They graded her feminism,"},{"time":355598,"text":"instead of simply taking a grown,\naccomplished woman at her word."},{"time":359890,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":362552,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365250,"text":"We demand perfection from feminists,"},{"time":367791,"text":"because we are still fighting for so much,"},{"time":370172,"text":"we want so much,"},{"time":371493,"text":"we need so damn much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373395,"text":"We go far beyond reasonable,\nconstructive criticism,"},{"time":376599,"text":"to dissecting any given woman's feminism,"},{"time":379372,"text":"tearing it apart\nuntil there's nothing left."},{"time":382253,"text":"We do not need to do that."},{"time":384452,"text":"Bad feminism -- or really, more inclusive\nfeminism -- is a starting point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388583,"text":"But what happens next?"},{"time":390592,"text":"We go from acknowledging\nour imperfections to accountability,"},{"time":394098,"text":"or walking the walk,\nand being a little bit brave."},{"time":397888,"text":"If I listen to degrading music,"},{"time":400216,"text":"I am creating a demand for which\nartists are more than happy"},{"time":403742,"text":"to contribute a limitless supply."},{"time":406120,"text":"These artists are not going to change\n"},{"time":408000,"text":"how they talk about women in their songs"},{"time":409955,"text":"until we demand that change\nby affecting their bottom line."},{"time":413998,"text":"Certainly, it is difficult."},{"time":416149,"text":"Why must it be so catchy?"},{"time":418561,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":422291,"text":"It's hard to make the better choice,"},{"time":424344,"text":"and it is so easy to justify a lesser one."},{"time":427164,"text":"But --"},{"time":428226,"text":"when I justify bad choices,"},{"time":430005,"text":"I make it harder for women\nto achieve equality,"},{"time":432948,"text":"the equality that we all deserve,"},{"time":434836,"text":"and I need to own that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436533,"text":"I think of my nieces, ages three and four."},{"time":439826,"text":"They are gorgeous\nand headstrong, brilliant girls,"},{"time":442289,"text":"who are a whole lot of brave."},{"time":444284,"text":"I want them to thrive in a world\nwhere they are valued"},{"time":447225,"text":"for the powerful creatures they are."},{"time":449577,"text":"I think of them,"},{"time":450656,"text":"and suddenly, the better choice\nbecomes far easier to make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454775,"text":"We can all make better choices."},{"time":457333,"text":"We can change the channel\nwhen a television show"},{"time":459830,"text":"treats sexual violence\nagainst women like sport,"},{"time":462548,"text":"Game of Thrones."},{"time":464000,"text":"We can change the radio station"},{"time":465834,"text":"when we hear songs\nthat treat women as nothing."},{"time":469063,"text":"We can spend our\nbox office dollars elsewhere"},{"time":471770,"text":"when movies don't treat women\n"},{"time":473320,"text":"as anything more than decorative objects."},{"time":475743,"text":"We can stop supporting professional sports"},{"time":478008,"text":"where the athletes treat \ntheir partners like punching bags."},{"time":482171,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487595,"text":"In other ways, men --\nand especially straight white men --"},{"time":490566,"text":"can say, \"No, I will not publish\nwith your magazine,"},{"time":493677,"text":"or participate in your project,\nor otherwise work with you,"},{"time":496987,"text":"until you include a fair number of women,"},{"time":499408,"text":"both as participants and decision makers."},{"time":502670,"text":"I won't work with you\nuntil your publication,"},{"time":504821,"text":"or your organization, is more inclusive\nof all kinds of difference.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":509225,"text":"Those of us who are underrepresented"},{"time":511542,"text":"and invited to participate\nin such projects,"},{"time":513735,"text":"can also decline to be included"},{"time":516128,"text":"until more of us are invited\nthrough the glass ceiling,"},{"time":519155,"text":"and we are tokens no more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521553,"text":"Without these efforts,"},{"time":523251,"text":"without taking these stands,"},{"time":525077,"text":"our accomplishments\nare going to mean very little."},{"time":528365,"text":"We can commit these small acts of bravery"},{"time":531002,"text":"and hope that our choices trickle\nupward to the people in power --"},{"time":534929,"text":"editors, movie and music producers,"},{"time":537564,"text":"CEOs, lawmakers --"},{"time":539961,"text":"the people who can make\nbigger, braver choices"},{"time":542198,"text":"to create lasting, meaningful change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545678,"text":"We can also boldly claim our feminism --"},{"time":548225,"text":"good, bad, or anywhere in between."},{"time":551329,"text":"The last line of my book\n\"Bad Feminist\" says,"},{"time":553805,"text":"\"I would rather be a bad feminist\nthan no feminist at all.\""},{"time":558240,"text":"This is true for so many reasons,"},{"time":560304,"text":"but first and foremost, I say this\nbecause once upon a time,"},{"time":563888,"text":"my voice was stolen from me,"},{"time":565741,"text":"and feminism helped me\nto get my voice back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569455,"text":"There was an incident."},{"time":570915,"text":"I call it an incident so I can carry\nthe burden of what happened."},{"time":574724,"text":"Some boys broke me,"},{"time":576136,"text":"when I was so young, I did not know\n"},{"time":577950,"text":"what boys can do to break a girl."},{"time":580400,"text":"They treated me like I was nothing."},{"time":582566,"text":"I began to believe I was nothing."},{"time":585064,"text":"They stole my voice, and in the after,"},{"time":587127,"text":"I did not dare to believe"},{"time":588508,"text":"that anything I might say could matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590948,"text":"But --"},{"time":591981,"text":"I had writing."},{"time":593377,"text":"And there, I wrote myself back together."},{"time":596242,"text":"I wrote myself toward a stronger\nversion of myself."},{"time":599653,"text":"I read the words of women"},{"time":601028,"text":"who might understand a story like mine,"},{"time":603384,"text":"and women who looked like me,"},{"time":605179,"text":"and understood what it was like to move\nthrough the world with brown skin."},{"time":609303,"text":"I read the words of women\nwho showed me I was not nothing."},{"time":613602,"text":"I learned to write like them,"},{"time":615308,"text":"and then I learned to write as myself."},{"time":617856,"text":"I found my voice again,"},{"time":619024,"text":"and I started to believe that my voice\nis powerful beyond measure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624048,"text":"Through writing and feminism,"},{"time":625610,"text":"I also found that if I was\na little bit brave,"},{"time":628388,"text":"another woman might hear me\nand see me and recognize"},{"time":632013,"text":"that none of us are the nothing\nthe world tries to tell us we are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636160,"text":"In one hand,"},{"time":637692,"text":"I hold the power to accomplish anything."},{"time":640740,"text":"And in my other,"},{"time":641765,"text":"I hold the humbling reality\nthat I am just one woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645918,"text":"I am a bad feminist,"},{"time":647621,"text":"I am a good woman,"},{"time":649287,"text":"I am trying to become better\nin how I think,"},{"time":651686,"text":"and what I say, and what I do,"},{"time":653970,"text":"without abandoning everything\nthat makes me human."},{"time":657152,"text":"I hope that we can all do the same."},{"time":659700,"text":"I hope that we can all be\na little bit brave,"},{"time":661967,"text":"when we most need such bravery."},{"time":664856,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}